Information
------------------------------

Ross Kemp Extreme World Series 5: Colombia
BAFTA-winning documentary maker Ross Kemp takes on important global issues of our time. Entering some of the world's most dangerous locations, he tells the untold stories of those suffering war, crime, violence and poverty.
In this episode Ross Kemp investigates how Colombia's drug trade is undermining the war-torn country's attempts to forge a peace accord after decades of civil war.
